{
  "stem": "26142.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we-- my father asked him to-- to give us a-- a written paper that we will-- we will move.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He had a sister that lived 70 kilometers deeper, close to the city of Khust.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We will take some belongings and send it over there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But we had to have a permit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He gave us a permit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And-- and-- the-- the other Jews saw what happened that-- that we are sending some-- some stuff away from the house.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And a panic broke out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But no-- nobody-- it-- it-- it's for your-- for your own good, but no, it was-- nobody is-- wants to leave a house where-- that he lives in and-- and built and everything for so many years, just-- just to leave it and leave and go.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But anyway, we did some stuff, clothing, we send out clothing, some-- some of-- of-- jewelry that-- that my mother had and my father had.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And my older brother, Tsvi, I forgot to mention, by that time already he got married with a girl from [?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Kalerne ?] and-- but he was in Torun, happened to be that time there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "So he-- we send him, and he went and-- and dropped this off to my father's sister, my-- our aunt.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And this happened about two or three weeks before August the 2nd, we did that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "When this officer told my father that, my older brother, Eliezer, his wife was a Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "He met her in the city of Debrecen and her mother was still alive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "So she decided-- they decided that she better-- it's too chokey up here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "We better go to Debrecen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And they have-- they had two children.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
